<lb n="0884c20"/>
<lb n="0884c21"/><head type="no">No. 1367</head><div1 type="jing">
<lb n="0884c22"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="001"/><jhead><note n="0884011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">【原】麗本</note>佛說大普賢陀羅尼<note n="0884012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">經＋（出廣濟眾生經第四卷中）夾註【元】</note><app n="0884012"><lem>經</lem><rdg wit="【元】" resp="Taisho">經<note place="inline">出廣濟眾生經第四卷中</note></rdg></app></jhead></juan>
<lb n="0884c23"/>
<lb n="0884c24"/><byline type="Translator"><note n="0884013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（舊）＋失【元】【明】</note><app n="0884013"><lem>失</lem><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">舊失</rdg></app>譯<note n="0884014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔人名今附梁錄〕－【宋】，人名今＝師名開元【元】【明】</note><app n="0884014"><lem>人名今附梁錄</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">師名開元附梁錄</rdg></app></byline>
<lb n="0884c25"/><p>如是我聞。一時佛在舍衛國祇樹給孤獨園。
<lb n="0884c26"/>時佛告阿難。吾今說大普賢&CB00057;。汝當受持</p>
<lb n="0884c27"/><p type="dharani">多擲多　阿&CB00062;　那&CB00062;　<note n="0884015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">茶＝荼【三】＊</note><note n="0884015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">茶＝荼【宋】＊【元】＊【明】＊</note><app n="0884015"><lem>茶</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">荼</rdg></app>彌<anchor id="fxT21p0884c01"/>茶　遮居梨
<lb n="0884c28"/>　居梨<anchor id="fxT21p0884c02"/>茶也　居梨<anchor id="fxT21p0884c03"/>茶也拔坻　思提　思
<lb n="0884c29"/>陀　婆夢坻</p><p type="inline">阿難此大普賢&CB00057;。遮滅一切
<pb ed="T" id="T21.1367.0885a" n="0885a"/>
<lb n="0885a01"/>兵刃。除一切怨<note n="0885001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">仇＋（諸怨）【三】</note><note n="0885001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">仇＋（諸怨）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0885001"><lem>仇</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">仇諸怨</rdg></app>。除一切夜叉羅剎復多等
<lb n="0885a02"/>畏。除一切不得食下鬼名</p>
<lb n="0885a03"/><p>胡摩兜<note place="inline">一</note>烏奢&CB00264;&CB00264;胡摩兜<note place="inline">二</note>阿&CB00145;羯卑胡摩
<lb n="0885a04"/>兜<note place="inline">三</note>破波羅胡摩兜<note place="inline">四</note>莎呵<note place="inline">五</note></p>
<lb n="0885a05"/><p>&CB00057;水七遍與病人飲之</p>
<lb n="0885a06"/><p>腰&CB00560;痛鬼名</p>
<lb n="0885a07"/><p>呼盧兜<note place="inline">一</note>波吒羅呼盧兜<note place="inline">二</note>毘<note n="0885002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">魔＝摩【明】</note><app n="0885002"><lem>魔</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">摩</rdg></app>羅呼盧兜<note place="inline">三</note>
<lb n="0885a08"/>彌梨耆梨卑呼盧兜<note place="inline">四</note>莎呵<note place="inline">五</note></p>
<lb n="0885a09"/><p>&CB00057;三色縷青黃綠。結作七結。繫&CB00560;腕次繫髀
<lb n="0885a10"/>後繫腰</p>
<lb n="0885a11"/><p>頭痛鬼名</p>
<lb n="0885a12"/><p>胡摩兜摩呵迦吒羅<note place="inline">一</note>毘摩迦吒羅<note place="inline">二</note>呼呼羅
<lb n="0885a13"/>迦吒羅<note place="inline">三</note>伊呼迦吒羅<note place="inline">四</note>伊<note n="0885003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">未＝末【三】</note><note n="0885003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">未＝末【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0885003"><lem>未</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">末</rdg></app>迦知迦吒羅<note place="inline">五</note>
<lb n="0885a14"/>莎呵<note place="inline">六</note></p>
<lb n="0885a15"/><p>七遍&CB00057;楊枝打二七下</p>
<lb n="0885a16"/><p>闇鈍鬼名</p>
<lb n="0885a17"/><p><note n="0885004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB01654;＝呼【三】</note><note n="0885004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">&CB01654;＝呼【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0885004"><lem>&CB01654;</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">呼</rdg></app>吒吒<note place="inline">一</note>浮律置浮吒吒<note place="inline">二</note>阿支拏呼吒吒<note place="inline">三</note>
<lb n="0885a18"/>浮律置支呼吒吒<note place="inline">四</note>伊呼破羅支呼吒吒<note place="inline">五</note>私
<lb n="0885a19"/>蜜兜伊呼支破羅<note place="inline">六</note>莎呵<note n="0885005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔七〕－【宋】</note><app n="0885005"><lem><note place="inline">七</note></lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0885a20"/><p>三七遍&CB00057;七日日三遍</p>
<lb n="0885a21"/><p>耳痛鬼名</p>
<lb n="0885a22"/><p>比膩波<note place="inline">一</note>阿制置毘膩波<note place="inline">二</note>呼膩置毘膩波<note place="inline">三</note>
<lb n="0885a23"/>伊呼支膩<note n="0885006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">置＋（毘）【元】【明】</note><app n="0885006"><lem>置</lem><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">置毘</rdg></app>膩波<note place="inline">四</note>耆摩膩<note n="0885007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（置）＋毘【元】【明】</note><app n="0885007"><lem>毘</lem><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">置毘</rdg></app>膩波<note place="inline">五</note>莎呵
<lb n="0885a24"/><note n="0885008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔六〕－【宋】</note><app n="0885008"><lem><note place="inline">六</note></lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0885a25"/><p>於月生一日。設使左耳痛南向坐。右耳痛北
<lb n="0885a26"/>向<note n="0885009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔坐〕－【宋】</note><app n="0885009"><lem>坐</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。東向門病人門內坐&CB00057;師門外坐。水亦
<lb n="0885a27"/>門<note n="0885010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">外＋（&CB00057;）【三】</note><note n="0885010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">外＋（&CB00057;）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0885010"><lem>外</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">外&CB00057;</rdg></app>二七遍三&CB01834;之</p>
<lb n="0885a28"/><p>淋鬼名</p>
<lb n="0885a29"/><p>破波羅<note place="inline">一</note>浮梨浮梨置破波羅<note place="inline">二</note>車<note n="0885011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">慕＝暮【三】</note><note n="0885011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">慕＝暮【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0885011"><lem>慕</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">暮</rdg></app>那破波
<pb ed="T" id="T21.1367.0885b" n="0885b"/>
<lb n="0885b01"/>羅<note place="inline">三</note>呼呼羅車波羅<note place="inline">四</note></p>
<lb n="0885b02"/><p>熱病鬼神病。方道蠱毒&CB00057;術。毘多<anchor id="fxT21p0885b01"/>茶富多
<lb n="0885b03"/>那等。善男子善女人所至之處。若行道中若
<lb n="0885b04"/>水道中若急難處應念此&CB00057;。無有夜叉復多
<lb n="0885b05"/>毘舍遮拘槃<anchor id="fxT21p0885b02"/>茶迦<note n="0885012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">吒＝&CB00062;【三】</note><note n="0885012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">吒＝&CB00062;【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0885012"><lem>吒</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&CB00062;</rdg></app>富多那羅剎毘多<anchor id="fxT21p0885b03"/>茶
<lb n="0885b06"/>等畏。又無水火刀杖兵凶毒藥衰害&CB00057;術方
<lb n="0885b07"/>道一切諸惡人非人等如是諸畏。阿難若有
<lb n="0885b08"/>恐怖急難。應誦念此&CB00057;。無能作衰惱者。復次
<lb n="0885b09"/>阿難若有受持讀誦此&CB00057;。如上天龍鬼神二
<lb n="0885b10"/>十八部人非人等。不能越犯此&CB00057;。鐵輪金剛
<lb n="0885b11"/>輪當為作苦患。令頭破作七分。四方四維上
<lb n="0885b12"/>下若。有於此人起惡心者。悉皆繫其毒心令
<lb n="0885b13"/>不發起。是善男子善女人。應善讀誦執持奉
<lb n="0885b14"/>行</p>
<lb n="0885b15"/><juan fun="close" n="001"><jhead>佛說大普賢陀羅尼經</jhead></juan></div1>
</body></text></TEI.2>
